
**Policy Name:** parkmycloud-for-one-account

**Policy Description:** The minimum permissions required to run ParkMyCloud:


{
    "Version": "2012-10-17",
    "Statement": [
        {
            "Action": [
                "ec2:StartInstances",
                "ec2:StopInstances"
            ],
            "Resource": [
                "arn:aws:ec2:*:<Your Account Number Here>:instance/*"
            ],
            "Effect": "Allow"
        },
        {
            "Action": [
                "iam:GetUser",
                "ec2:Describe*"
            ],
            "Resource": [
                "*"
            ],
            "Effect": "Allow"
        }
    ]
}

NOTE: Your acount number is the 12-digit number found in the User ARN string. For example:

User ARN: arn:aws:iam::0123456789012:user/ernie

The account number would be 0123456789012